# Components Directory Guide

The [src/components](mdc:web/src/components) directory contains reusable UI and logic components for the web app.

## Subfolders
- **[ui](mdc:web/src/components/ui)**: Shared UI elements (e.g., [button.tsx](mdc:web/src/components/ui/button.tsx), [modal.tsx](mdc:web/src/components/ui/modal.tsx), [sidebar.tsx](mdc:web/src/components/ui/sidebar.tsx)).
- **[modals](mdc:web/src/components/modals)**: Modal dialog components (e.g., [alert-modal.tsx](mdc:web/src/components/modals/alert-modal.tsx)).
- **[editor](mdc:web/src/components/editor)**: Editor-related components (e.g., [EditorComponent.tsx](mdc:web/src/components/editor/EditorComponent.tsx)).
- **[oauth](mdc:web/src/components/oauth)**: OAuth login components (e.g., [GoogleLoginButton.tsx](mdc:web/src/components/oauth/GoogleLoginButton.tsx)).

## Example Components
- [product-option-dialog.tsx](mdc:web/src/components/product-option-dialog.tsx): Product option selection dialog.
- [cart-item-info.tsx](mdc:web/src/components/cart-item-info.tsx): Displays information about a cart item.
- [global-navbar.tsx](mdc:web/src/components/global-navbar.tsx): Main navigation bar.

For a full list, see the [components directory](mdc:web/src/components).
